creator: Luum
descriptionHtml:
Get quick and easy access to your commuter benefits with Luum.

No matter how you get to work, use the commute calendar to log your daily trips. See past activity and personal commute statistics from within the app. Get easy access to many of the features you know and love from your company’s commute hub. Also, we’re going to be constantly adding more features to improve your commuting experience – stay tuned!

Please note: the Luum app is only functional for employees whose companies use Luum to manage commuter benefits. To learn more about Luum and get your company signed up, check out our website!
